{
  "stem": "19211.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we were trading-- always trading that for food, bread, some eggs, stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we were very fortunate till about '42.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about me, my brother and my father, and my mom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The four of us, we stayed together all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just have one brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have one sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was born after the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But just one brother, a younger one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then we moved to Ponikwa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name of the place was, was called Ponikwa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "P--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "P-O-N-I-K-W-A, Ponikwa.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a lucky streak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved there in 1940-- close to '42, I think is right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is about 20, 30 miles from Brody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to order-- I'll come to you later.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go on vacations in the summertime before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was big-- there were big forests with pine trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- and I had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had bronchitis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the doctor said it's good for me to get away there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We went there in the summer, and we stayed there for the whole summer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was breathing better there, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The air was clear, and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed in a-- we rented a house from a farmer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we stayed in that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were looking for customers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a few other families that came there, not only Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were Polish and Jewish families that came there and-- for a vacation in summertime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the happiest-- even during, during the war-- it was the happiest time of our year-- of, of our-- of my life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We didn't see much Germans there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next, we got the word that it's getting bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know how bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
